## Blueprint routes confirmed live
- `GET /clientfinder/leads` — paginated lead list
- `POST /clientfinder/leads` — create lead
- `PATCH /clientfinder/leads/<id>` — update outreach status/notes
- `DELETE /clientfinder/leads/<id>` — remove lead
- `GET /clientfinder/leads/export` — CSV export
- `GET /clientfinder/leads/stats` — aggregate stats (50 seeded leads, 6 industries)

## handoff
- produced: both repos pushed and verified live; demo at `/demos/client-finder-1-0/` (200), backend at `/clientfinder/leads/stats` (200 with seeded data)
- decisions: SPA 404 on `/work-samples/client-finder-1-0` is correct behavior on GH Pages (handled by 404.html redirect); not a defect
- next needs: deploy-test should exercise live demo UI in browser + POST/PATCH/GET lead CRUD via the live API endpoint
- risks: ONNX WASM (21.6 MB) may time out on slow connections before WebGPU inference loads; demo gracefully falls back to mock scores
